Subject: insect mesothoracic segment
Value: The insect body segment that corresponds to the mesothorax and is posterior to the insect prothoracic segment.@en

Subject: insect metathoracic segment
Value: The insect body segment that corresponds to the mesothorax and is posterior to the insect prothoracic segment.@en

Subject: encircles
Value: x encircles y if both x and y are regions of the 2D structure z, or 2D cross-sections of a 3D object z, and the boundary of y on z is exclusively continuous with x.@en

Subject: encircled by
Value: y is encircled by x if both x and y are regions of the 2D structure z, or 2D cross-sections of a 3D object z, and the boundary of y on z is exclusively continuous with y.@en

Subject: encircles via conjunctiva
Value: sclerite A encircles_via_conjunctiva sclerite B if A is encircled_via_conjuntiva X that encircles B@en

Subject: encircled via conjunctiva
Value: sclerite B is encircled_via_conjunctiva if sclerite A encircles_via_conjuntiva X sclerite B@en
